<<COND_NOT_MD>>Define_Com Class(#PRIM_LIST.String) Name(#Column2) Columnunits(Proportion) Columnwidth(1) Displayposition(2) Parent(#DropDownofLocations) Source(#STD_STRNG) Columnvisible(False)

